flowchart LR
  I1[User Audio Input]
  STT[Whisper STT\nWebGPU or WASM]
  C1[Context Manager\nRAG Retrieval plus Prompt Assembly]
  LLM[WebLLM Llama 3.2\nToken Generation]
  TTS[Piper TTS\nWASM or Native]
  O1[Audio Output]

  I1 --> STT
  STT --> C1
  C1 --> LLM
  LLM --> TTS
  TTS --> O1

  R1[Memory Store and Vector Index] --> C1
  C1 --> R1

